 reproduce\nsmooth and coherent bubbles as observed. Because the dynamical influence and\nheating of the ICM critically depend on the bubble morphology, our study\nhighlights the fundamental role of \"microphysics\" on the macroscopic properties\nof AGN feedback processes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Sep 2019 17:59:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Sep 2019 15:42:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-02"}
