, the\nabsolute carrier phase of mid-infrared pulses can be fixed within 200 mrad and\nerrors in the measurement of phase-sensitive responses can be reduced to within\n1 fs over a few tens of hours.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Sep 2019 09:22:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-13"}
